Reason: Keep terminal hyperlink handling compatible with internal terminal environments.
Owner: DataWorks Qwen Code maintainers
Patch-Base: cc800d01322c3bf642b919425576da09f182c3d5
Fork-Ref: origin/main (c6b168ec034253e76a07492a30cfb134eae47545)
Upstream-Ref: upstream/main
Paths:
  - packages/cli/src/ui/utils/osc8.test.ts
  - packages/cli/src/ui/utils/osc8.ts
